  "titleCh": "燒墾",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "所謂燒墾？燒墾是以前老人家為了生活的重要工作之一。首先尋找荒蕪或在山坡地之地，雜草叢生，可以砍伐草木。但經燒墾後的荒地，就可以種植農作物，這就是燒墾法。",
      "ab": "O mingilap hananay i, o tadakalimelaan a demak no malitengay to saka’orip iti:ya ho ko mingilapay. Sa’ayaw mikilimay to masafaniyotay anca o masa’apilisay a pala, oya makarengorengosay, nga’ayay a fariwen. Mahalek to a mingilap koni a kohkoh, nga’ayay to a paloma to pinaloma, o mingilapay hananay konini.",
