    {
      "chinese": "等到灰燼都化為泥土狀後，開始挖地種植種子灑在土壤裡，如綠豆、花生或撒稻米及小米的種子。撒種子之後，再用掃帚掃使之被埋入土地之下。等到下過雨之後，種的植物便會長新芽了。",
      "ab": "Maedeng to mala’afo kora sota’, satapan to a micoray to sera a mifelesak to sapal, tinako o naniwac, kodasing anca folesaken ko sapal no panay ato falinono. Maharek to a mifolesak to sapal, tano saasiken a miasik a milafong i lalinik no sota’. Ma’orad sato i, cicengo’ to ko mipalomaan a pinaloma.",
